 <span data-ttu-id="db53e-127">사실은 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> 개체는 형식으로 마샬링할 수 없는 `VT_ERROR` COM에서 다시 전달 된 후</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db53e-127">Note that <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> objects are not marshaled as type `VT_ERROR` after they are passed back from COM.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="db53e-128">단일 값을 형식으로 COM에서 다시 마샬링될 `VT_I4`반면 배열 형식으로 COM에서 다시 마샬링됩니다 `VT_UI4`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db53e-128">A single value is marshaled back from COM as type `VT_I4`, while arrays are marshaled back from COM as type `VT_UI4`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="db53e-129">에 대 한 자세한 `VT_ERROR`에 대 한 기존 설명서를 참조 하십시오 `VARENUM::VT_ERROR` MSDN 라이브러리에서.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db53e-129">For more information on `VT_ERROR`, please see the existing documentation for `VARENUM::VT_ERROR` in the MSDN library.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="db53e-130">다음 코드 예제에서는 먼저 보여 줍니다는 유일한 <xref:System.Int32> 개체에서 COM에 마샬링될는 <xref:System.Int32> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db53e-130">The following code example first demonstrates a lone <xref:System.Int32> object marshaled back from COM as an <xref:System.Int32> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="db53e-131">다음 방법을 보여 줍니다는 <xref:System.Int32> 배열에서 COM에 마샬링될는 <xref:System.UInt32> 배열입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db53e-131">It then demonstrates an <xref:System.Int32> array marshaled back from COM as a <xref:System.UInt32> array.</span></span>  
  
```  
// Scenario 1:  
// Pass a single value.  
Int32 x = 3;  
Object o = new ErrorWrapper(x);  
// Pass 'o' to COM.  
// On the return trip, 'o' has been unwrapped and is still an Int32 object.  
Int32 y = (Int32)o;  
Scenario 2:  
// Pass an array of values.  
Int32[] arr = new Int32[3];  
Object o = new ErrorWrapper(arr);  
// Pass 'o' to COM.  
// On the return trip, 'o' has been unwrapped and is now a UInt32[] array.  
UInt32[ ] arr2 = (UInt32[])o;  
```
